title: Willie Nelson - The Willie Way (1972) [FLAC]
description:
downloaded from Qobuz

Classic Willie Nelson songwriting fills this album (except for two covers) with performances as only he knows how. "You Left Me a Long, Long Time Ago" is worth the price of this record alone. Also, Willie's version of "Undo the Right" is easily as good as Johnny Bush's 1968 hit. ~ Jim Worbois, Allmusic
